<paragraph blockId="4.[826,1429,311,1235]" pageId="4" pageNumber="250">
General distribution: Antilles, 
<collectingCountry box="[1226,1375,825,849]" name="Guadeloupe" pageId="4" pageNumber="250">Guadeloupe</collectingCountry>
: un- der shrubs near the sea (
<bibRefCitation author="Mahunka S." box="[1114,1306,860,884]" pageId="4" pageNumber="250" pagination="119 - 144" refId="ref8132" refString="Mahunka S. 1985 a - Neue und interessante Milben aus dem Genfer Museum LVII. Oribatida Americana 9: Antilles I (Acari) - Revue suisse de Zoologie, 92: 119 - 144." type="journal article" year="1985">Mahunka 1985a</bibRefCitation>
); 
<collectingCountry box="[1325,1424,860,884]" name="Ecuador" pageId="4" pageNumber="250">Ecuador</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingRegion box="[826,1048,895,919]" country="Ecuador" name="Galapagos" pageId="4" pageNumber="250">Galapagos Islands</collectingRegion>
: under 
<taxonomicName box="[1151,1257,896,919]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Aizoaceae" genus="Sesuvium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="4" pageNumber="250" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1151,1257,896,919]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="250">Sesuvium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
shrubs in the littoral zone on Santa Cruz Island, in leaf litter of a dense elfin-forest on VolcAEn Alcedo (Isabela Island), in fern litter and moss near a fumarole on Fernandina Island (
<bibRefCitation author="Schatz H." box="[1060,1202,1035,1060]" pageId="4" pageNumber="250" pagination="69 - 84" refId="ref8584" refString="Schatz H. 1993 - The genus Lohmannia (Acari: Oribatida: Lohmanniidae) in the Galapagos Islands - Acarologia, 34: 69 - 84." type="journal article" year="1993">Schatz 1993</bibRefCitation>
); Central America: 
<collectingCountry box="[826,896,1071,1095]" name="Belize" pageId="4" pageNumber="250">Belize</collectingCountry>
Light House Reef: Half Moon Cay, in leaf litter (
<bibRefCitation author="Schatz H." box="[900,1120,1106,1130]" pageId="4" pageNumber="250" pagination="267 - 287" refId="ref8647" refString="Schatz H. 1994 b - Lohmanniidae (Acari: Oribatida) from the Galapagos Islands, the Cocos Island, and Central America - Acarologia, 35: 267 - 287." type="journal article" year="1994">Schatz 1994b: 276</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Schatz H." box="[1137,1280,1106,1130]" pageId="4" pageNumber="250" pagination="209 - 288" refId="ref8721" refString="Schatz H. 2006 - Catalogue of known oribatid mite species (Acari: Oribatida) from the Central American landbridge (First part) - Tropical Zoology, 19: 209 - 288." type="journal article" year="2006">Schatz 2006</bibRefCitation>
); 
<collectingCountry box="[1304,1367,1106,1130]" name="Cuba" pageId="4" pageNumber="250">Cuba</collectingCountry>
Ciudad de 
<collectingRegion box="[924,1059,1141,1165]" country="Cuba" name="La Habana" pageId="4" pageNumber="250">La Habana</collectingRegion>
, Santiago de las Vegas, sugar cane (
<taxonomicName box="[894,1070,1176,1200]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Saccharum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="4" pageNumber="250" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="undetermined">
<emphasis box="[894,1013,1176,1200]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="250">Saccharum</emphasis>
spp.
</taxonomicName>
), leaf litter and soil (
<bibRefCitation author="Prieto D. &amp; Calderon L." pageId="4" pageNumber="250" pagination="144 - 145" refId="ref8510" refString="Prieto D., Calderon L. 1992 - Registros de nuevos taxa de AEcaros oribAEtidos (Acari: Cryptostigmata) para Cuba - Revista Biologia, La Habana (Cuba), 6: 144 - 145." type="journal article" year="1992">Prieto and Calderón 1992</bibRefCitation>
); first record for 
<collectingCountry box="[1193,1305,1211,1235]" name="Bermuda" pageId="4" pageNumber="250">Bermuda</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
